name: Timetable generator
tagline: Generates a timetable for our university using a genetic algorithm
body:
Timetabling is done manually in our university, Amrita Vishwa Vidyapeetham, Ettimadai, Coimbatore. It is a pretty tedious process with more than 3 faculty involved for more than 3 months and still a healthy solution is hard to come across. This project aims to solve that problem using a genetic algorithm.

The people involved in contributing to the project are  
[Sambhav Jain](https://github.com/zeus9/)  
[Siddarth Jawahar](https://github.com/basusisa/)
